                <mxCell id="mod-issue-validation" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;(3) Issue Management &amp;amp; Validation Module&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;• Issue Raised in iCAPS: &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Assigned Severity (Anticipated Frequency, Significance of Impact); &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;CAP created with Owner, Type &amp;amp; Business Target Date; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;4Cs documented (Concern, Cause, Consequence, Context)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;• Issue &amp;amp; CAP Lifecycle Tracking: &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;CAP types — Planning / Compensating / Remediation / Sustainability; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;tracked to completion against Business Target Date; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Assign Issue Owner &amp;amp; Coordinator&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;• Issue Validation (IV Workflow — CIA Module): &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;IV Document submitted → &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Validation Passes? → &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Pending Approval (L1 Single-Step or L2 Two-Step: Review Mgr → Senior Mgr) → &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Approved → &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;iCAPS Sync&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Outcome: &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Successful Validation = Issue Closed in iCAPS | &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Failed Validation = Issue Re-Opened | &lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;New Edit Needed = Clone to new Draft (version N+1)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#FDEDEC;strokeColor=#C0392B;" parent="processing-section" vertex="1">
